OL,3,CPlans to cut number of politicians and
OL,4,Cchange elections in Alderney
OL,6,FThe number of politicians elected in
OL,7,FAlderney could be cut from ten to
OL,8,Feight.
OL,10,FIt is part of a package of government
OL,11,Freforms agreed by the island's Policy
OL,12,Fand Finance Committee (P&F).
OL,14,FAlso on the table are plans to reduce
OL,15,Fthe number of seats that can be
OL,16,Fcontested at November's election from
OL,17,Ffive to three, offering those who are
OL,18,Fsuccessful two-year terms.
