OL,3,CPlans to cut number of politicians and
OL,4,Cchange elections in Alderney
OL,6,FThis would then allow an election for
OL,7,Fall eight seats every four years from
OL,8,FNovember 2028.
OL,10,FIn a press statement, Members say this
OL,11,Fwould "reduce election costs and
OL,12,Fincrease continuity".
OL,14,FMeanwhile, P&F want the public to
OL,15,Fshare their views on how the island
OL,16,Fchooses its two representatives in the
OL,17,FStates of Guernsey.
OL,19,FCurrently, plebiscite public elections
OL,20,Fare held twice a year to signal
OL,21,Fpopular support for members.
