OL,3,CPlans to cut number of politicians and
OL,4,Cchange elections in Alderney
OL,6,FAppointments are then confirmed each
OL,7,FJanuary by the States of Alderney,
OL,8,Fwith two backup representatives also
OL,9,Fselected.
OL,11,FThis process was brought in on a trial
OL,12,Fbasis in 2006, but has continued until
OL,13,Fthe present day - with P&F asking
OL,14,F"whether it should be legally
OL,15,Fimplemented or discontinued".
