OL,3,CPlans to cut number of politicians and
OL,4,Cchange elections in Alderney
OL,6,FP&F has decided to keep the island's
OL,7,Fexisting committee system after
OL,8,Fconsidering other political models,
OL,9,Fincluding an executive council which
OL,10,Fhas been mooted over the past few
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FJeannie Cameron, Chair of P&F and
OL,14,FPolitical Lead for Government Reform,
OL,15,Fsays the proposals, if brought in,
OL,16,Fwill "streamline decision making and
OL,17,Fimprove efficiencies".
