OL,3,CPlans to cut number of politicians and
OL,4,Cchange elections in Alderney
OL,6,FShe adds: "Many of these issues
OL,7,Ffeatured in Members' election
OL,8,Fmanifestos and have been debated for a
OL,9,Flong period of time.
OL,11,F"Governance reform in Alderney is not
OL,12,Fnew, and significant work and several
OL,13,Frounds of discussion have taken place
OL,14,Fto reach the point we arrived at this
OL,15,Fweek."
OL,17,FThe proposed reforms will now be
OL,18,Fsubmitted to the Law Officers for
OL,19,Fconsideration, with a public
OL,20,Fconsultation on the plebiscite
OL,21,Felections set to start soon.
